s: So, get ALL the protective gear before you ride! (The kids are on a hard surface and it doesn't take much to get a serious injury!) Get the helmet, wrist guards, knee/elbow pads (Triple 8 has good wrist guards/pads sets for this, try on for size in sporting goods store, and get skate helmet not pointed bike helmet) ... And then have fun...
